source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_00<tab>Teteroon has places for you to go and thingies for you to get.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_00<tab>メメルン交易商店のテテルンは、冒険者に手伝ってほしいことがあるようだ。

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_01<tab>Teteroon has asked that you help him brew Qiqirn firewater. To do so, slay coeurl pups to obtain three coeurl pup whiskers.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_01<tab><var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E86D201 /var>を作る手伝いを頼まれた。高地ラノシアの愚か者の滝付近にいる「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) 1D01 /var>」を討伐して「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E904101 /var>」を3本入手しよう。

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_02<tab>You have procured the required ingredients. Take them back to Teteroon.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_02<tab>メメルン交易商店の「テテルン」に集めた材料を渡そう。

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_03<tab>Teteroon has set about brewing his Qiqirn firewater from the ingredients you have provided. But good firewater takes time. Speak to him again later to learn how his concoction turns out.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_03<tab>冒険者の集めてきた材料で、<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E86D201 /var>の仕込みができた。完成までは少し時間がかかるらしい。

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TODO_00<tab>Slay coeurl pups and collect coeurl pup whiskers.
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the coeurl pup whiskers to Teteroon.
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SYSTEM_100_000<tab>To accept this quest, you must abandon the current main scenario quest. Open the corresponding entry in the journal or duty list and select “Abandon.”
target:
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SYSTEM_100_000<tab>受注するには、進行中のメインクエストを破棄する必要があります。
メインコマンドの「コンテンツ情報」から、
「ジャーナル」を選び、破棄してください。

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_000<tab>Good Buscaroon help Teteroon. Teteroon dead without good Buscaroon. Must give thankies. Many, many thankies. Teteroon make Qiqirn firewater for Buscaroon! Buscaroon love firewater!
target:
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_000<tab>テテルン、バスカロンに、お礼するっちゃ。
バスカロン、「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E86D201 /var>」好きだったっちゃ。
酒酒、もりもり、作るっちゃ。

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_001<tab>You help Teteroon make firewater? Need thingies to make. Need many, many thingies.
target:
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_001<tab>いっしょに、酒酒、作るっちゃ？
酒酒、材料、取ってくるっちゃ。

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_002<tab>Need coeurl pup whiskers. Need three good coeurl pup whiskers.
target:
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_002<tab>テテルン、美味しい水水、用意するっちゃ。
その間、「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) 1D01 /var>」倒して、
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E904101 /var>」、3本、取ってくるっちゃ。

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_020<tab>Teteroon make firewater for Buscaroon. You bring thingies Teteroon need?
target:
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_020<tab>酒酒、もりもり、作るっちゃ。
……材料、もりもり、取ってきたっちゃ？

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_021<tab>You brought all thingies! Teteroon make firewater now. Make good firewater for good Buscaroon.
target:
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_021<tab>酒酒、材料、そろったっちゃ！
テテルン、感謝で、いっぱいだっちゃ！

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_022<tab>Teteroon start making firewater now. Good firewater take time. More time, more good. You come back later.
target:
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_022<tab>さっそく、酒酒、作るっちゃ。
酒酒、できるの、待ってるっちゃ。
少しの間、待ってるっちゃ。
